PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (CARCROSS/TAGISH FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) provides for the withdrawal from disposal of certain tracts of land in the Yukon Territory until March 31, 2008, and (b) repeals a previous Withdrawal from Disposal Order made on December 13, 2001.
